        {
            "title": "人均消費¥4000吃象糞啃樹葉  上海餐廳主打「原始」風",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"上海餐廳主打「原始」風，人均消費¥4000元讓客人吃象糞啃樹葉。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/67d7d0255c752a1eaba8d8ba7c602256/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250412/_2025041218101253296.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">上海餐廳主打「原始」風，人均消費¥4000元讓客人吃象糞啃樹葉。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>上海一間高級餐廳讓顧客啃樹葉、舔冰塊，吃酸螞蟻、大象糞便，人均消費近4000元（人民幣，下同），而餐廳老闆分別來自雲南和法國，主打雨林味道餐點。不過有體驗過的博主狂吐槽「太儀式化」。\n\n</p><h2>用餐儀式感滿滿</h2>\n<p>據新民晚報報道，該餐廳熱植環繞、水霧繚繞、菜色原始，主打生態融合料理，2名老闆來自雲南和法國，想還原雨林味道。第一道開胃菜是讓食客從盆栽上剪片葉子，蘸上調料生吃。另有一盤冰塊，要客人舔掉上面的蜂蜜和花粉，主菜有苔蘚、竹蟲、酸螞蟻等，其中一道「鮮花插在香糞上」是將大象便便消毒乾燥輾碎做成甜品。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191707/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"餐廳讓客人在一盤冰塊上舔蜂蜜和花粉。新民晚報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cadf902d7863e9b461d61224aa02110c/2025-04/Clipboard49_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        餐廳讓客人在一盤冰塊上舔蜂蜜和花粉。新民晚報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191708/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"客人從盆栽上剪片葉子，蘸上調料生吃。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/11cc30ddbb2341423a11a6060d14879b/2025-04/Clipboard50_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        客人從盆栽上剪片葉子，蘸上調料生吃。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191709/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"模仿當地河流生態環境的鹹腥味飲品。 新民晚報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f48be587ec296ccf585f21505668cd3/2025-04/Clipboard51_1.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        模仿當地河流生態環境的鹹腥味飲品。 新民晚報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191710/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"「鮮花插在象糞上」。 快科技\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aee302195fde551e7606e6bdb6f31bd5/2025-04/Clipboard52_1.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「鮮花插在象糞上」。 快科技\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191711/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"模擬寄生花腐臭味道的糊糊。新民晚報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e3933aa54151df6725fbad94b567fc3f/2025-04/Clipboard53_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        模擬寄生花腐臭味道的糊糊。新民晚報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191712/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"食物由電動滑軌運上來。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d17423313937f92529bdfc39e1642cd/2025-04/Clipboard54_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        食物由電動滑軌運上來。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4191713/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大象糞做的甜品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d627429b1090f2201be98158fcd411c/2025-04/Clipboard55_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大象糞做的甜品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-topics/3439024/\">天價中菜｜上海一餐廳半隻雞賣￥480元 稱其「喝牛奶聽音樂長大」</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>整個用餐過程也是儀式感滿滿，吃頓飯得繞餐廳走兩圈，要參觀食材展示室、種著蔬菜的溫室、像登山一樣爬樓進入甜品台，食物是由電動滑軌運上來的。\n\n</p>\n<p>據悉，該餐廳每周只開2天，每晚僅開放1桌，有12個位子，提供15道體驗餐，一位要付3888元人民幣，菜單會不定時更新。\n\n</p>\n<p>至於餐點好不好吃，有吃過的網友表示，很難說每道都好吃，有些菜難以形容，幸好最好五道是正常料理，有雞腿類主食，至少能吃飽。也有不少博主吐槽，吃飯像是「參加了一場行為藝術」、「我們不以好吃為唯一標準，請大家抱著探險的心態吧」、「這簡直就是過度儀式感的典範」。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063583/即時-中國-人均消費¥4000吃象糞啃樹葉-上海餐廳主打-原始-風",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-13 07:36:13",
            "source": "stheadline",
