            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "意甲｜堅恩夠弗  費倫天拿必施絆「馬」索",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"堅恩近3場各賽共入4球。 REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9402bbb699a9217a2f91509491fb71c9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250412/_2025041220501292265.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">堅恩近3場各賽共入4球。 REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h4>足智彩球賽編號：FB0310<br/>\n費倫天拿 VS 帕爾馬<br/>\nHOY76台今晚9:00直播<br/>\n推介：讓球[-0.5/-1]主勝，波膽2:1及3:1</h4>\n<p>費倫天拿近期越戰越勇，周中在歐協聯賽事盡遣後備兵下，仍輕鬆贏波，今晚返回聯賽於主場對帕爾馬時幾乎可以全力搶分，尤其首席射手摩斯堅恩今季把握力非常穩定，讓球盤紫百合僅少讓半球/一球，「主勝」手到拿來。\n\n</p>\n<p>主隊費倫天拿近期接連擊敗祖雲達斯和阿特蘭大等前列分子，上周聯賽作客在領先兩球下，僅被AC米蘭2:2逼和，若非球隊全場失掉5個黃金機會，應已取得3連勝。中鋒摩斯堅恩今季在聯賽射入17球，近期連同國際賽，個人對上3場取得4個入球，腳風大順而且產量穩定，不難在今仗對帕爾馬的賽事中，再添進帳兼助紫百合贏波而回。\n\n</p><h3>紫百合頻挫勁旅</h3>\n<p>客隊帕爾馬上場聯賽在主場落後2球下逼和國際米蘭，錄得4連和，鬥志仍在今場或可破蛋，波膽2:1及3:1亦值得冷敲。馬高\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063616/即時-體育-意甲-堅恩夠弗-費倫天拿必施絆-馬-索",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-13 07:11:25",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "天文台｜短暫時間有陽光及非常乾燥 日間最高氣溫約24度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0e032a9a8cfb2e29ef9b2ed86ed46ffe/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250413/_2025041306473238304.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股強烈東北季候風正影響廣東沿岸，該區非常乾燥。此外，受沙塵天氣影響，廣東部分地區能見度較低。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，短暫時間有陽光及非常乾燥，部分地區能見度較低。日間最高氣溫約24度。初時吹清勁偏北風，離岸吹強風，高地間中達烈風程度。稍後風勢緩和。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望未來兩三日大致天晴及非常乾燥，日夜溫差頗大。本週後期天氣較為潮濕。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192257/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d9adcbf37981a87ce833f4f53ad136f8/2025-04/2025-04-13_06_32_07.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192258/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2cb9402ed3e8099c4e05cbed30ba60ff/2025-04/2025-04-13_06_32_41.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192259/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"短暫時間有陽光及非常乾燥。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1262a164083e2946d73f67238ea76b4a/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-13-06-29-09_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        短暫時間有陽光及非常乾燥。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192260/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間最高氣溫約24度。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6846a0bb392c3a3c99b2ba00c4ceec39/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-13-06-29-00_001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間最高氣溫約24度。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192261/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"展望未來兩三日大致天晴及非常乾燥。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a1527e6bd24221a7bd52b90a43662e8e/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-13-06-29-14_007.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        展望未來兩三日大致天晴及非常乾燥。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>受乾燥的東北季候風影響，廣東沿岸今早風勢頗大，日間天色好轉。隨著季候風在今日稍後緩和，未來兩三日廣東地區風勢微弱，普遍晴朗，日夜溫差頗大。預料一股偏南氣流會在本週中後期逐漸影響沿岸地區，該區天氣較為潮濕。而一道低壓槽會在本週後期為華南內陸地區帶來驟雨。\n\n</p>\n<p>天文台凌晨4時 45分發出特別天氣提示，預料本港吹偏北強風。市民應提防海面大浪可能帶來的危險。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063633/即時-港聞-天文台-短暫時間有陽光及非常乾燥-日間最高氣溫約24度",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-13 06:56:16",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "青衣私家車自炒反肚 兩女受傷自行爬出 清醒送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"其中一名女傷者坐在地上等待救援。網上圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f54dee9c26c05a2de23657a0c50798fc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250413/_2025041306212639037.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">其中一名女傷者坐在地上等待救援。網上圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>青衣發生交通意外。今日（13日）凌晨2時許，一輛白色私家車沿青衣西北交匯處行駛，當途至通往大山難竹金山與青衣的分岔路口時，懷疑突然失控，私家車撞欄後翻覆「 四輪朝天」，有途經駕駛者代為報警。\n\n</p>\n<p>救援人員接報趕至，車上女司機及女乘客已自行爬出車廂待救，她們均有受傷，清醒由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理。警方正調查事件。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192255/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"青衣私家車自炒兩女子受傷。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d9bd1c83b3743601d4e744af0f5416f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-12_at_23_02_40.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        青衣私家車自炒兩女子受傷。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>從網上圖片可見，其中一名女傷者意外後坐在地上等待救援。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
